<br>
He could <br>
<br>
1. Save up and buy a pair in the bazaar  or market when one became available (they are not no drop  here)<br>
<br>
2. Pay an appropriate level character to get the parts for him (again they are not no drop)<br>
<br>
<br>
3. pay for a traditional MQ which is the worst of three options.<br>
