<br>
     I've been examining the Firiona Vie boards with some interest, as I've been considering creating a character there after being somewhat disapointed with the quality of players on other servers.  By my nature, I'm very fond of tradeskills and crafting, and I'm often looking for new opportunties to sell my wares.<br>
<br>
     The FAQ notes that use of the auction line in &quot;inappropriate&quot; areas is often considered distasteful, and I was curious as to what most people would consider inappropriate.  I'm most active on the auction line when there is a bank nearby (ie, in town areas), or in areas that are frequently passed through on the way to towns (East Commons, Butcherblock, Misty Thicket, etc).  I'm not fond of the bazaar, it's much too impersonal for me, and I create most items at the specific request of a customer.<br>
<br>
     Would anyone consider the zones I've mentioned inappropriate for the auction line?  I don't want to inadventantly trangress any social conventions that may exist.<br>
<br>
     Many thanks,<br>
<br>
               Teellox <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=borblefootfurtoe>borblefoot furtoe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 116<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/18/03 10:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2942.topic&index=27>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Appropriate areas for auction line?</span><hr size=1> Auction used to be restricted to City zones, East commons, Greater Faydark. This was pre-luclin With the addition of luclin you can include the Bazaar, City zones and nexus could be added to the list. These restrictions were removed and although you can auction anywhere now. You may get frowned at using auction outside of the above mentioned zones. I am not sure where the Plane of knowledge and plane of tranquility fit in this picture.<br>
